king, not hearing the tapping at all. He wasn&#039;t even looking in that direction, so he was slightly startled at the tapping on his shoulder. He turns and looks at Copper. &quot;Yeah...where&#039;d you...&quot; He turns ahead and doesn&#039;t bother asking. &quot;Yeah. Where&#039;re you headed?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1396663343";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cc9f52";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13966453449";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8a2f19";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:433773;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"433773";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7850";s:6:"handle";s:12:"Copper_Relic";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"523";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Atlas_Parch";s:4:"text";s:476:"/me lag-lags, not so much! And way to eat a pizza by saying that! Anytime I try to not be so serious. Anyways, Copper went out after the tapping didn&#039;t work. Laughing at the startledness, he tilted his head and decided to be a bit creepy, &quot;Oh. I&#039;ve been tailing you all day, on the rooftops. I&#039;m part of the assassin&#039;s guild.&quot; He nodded and shrugged, &quot;I was about to go off a bad knight, but then I saw you, so I figured it could wait.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1396663893";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff7700";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13966458927";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#9b4900";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:433791;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"433791";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7579";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Atlas_Parch";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"524";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:12:"Copper_Relic";s:4:"text";s:455:"/me doesn&#039;t like to prove herself right, but: &quot;02:24:19 PM Jade_Array: I&#039;ll post first for both &#039;cause you know.&quot; Hmm? That doesn&#039;t even make sense about the pizza, but now I want pizza. Atlas made a face, leaning away from Copper. &quot;What..? W...Why?&quot; He steps away from Copper. &quot;Don&