t me started on Christin *drools more because only two females remotely attractive in the movie* Mhm. Dauntless all the way, I could totes survive there. It would be fun. You, me, Rea, some more guys because awkward reasons. We all get tats together. Yeah. Copper blinked as he heard something, turning his head, seeing Atlas, ignoring him, &quot;Shut up nub!&quot; He kept walking.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1396667622";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff7700";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13966496219";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#9b4900";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:434105;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"434105";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7579";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Atlas_Parch";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"524";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:12:"Copper_Relic";s:4:"text";s:280:"/me slaps. Also it&#039;s true. I mean, there were others...right? Tori? Tori. But she only showe up like twice. Yeah. Sure. If you make the train jump. &quot;Shut up, Copper.&quot; He says, stretching an pulling out a book, no matter how hard he tried to think of something else.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1396667776";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cc9f52";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13966497782";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8a2f19";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:434120;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"434120";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7850";s:6:"handle";s:12:"Copper_Relic";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"523";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Atlas_Parch";s:4:"text";s:365:"/me slapslaps. And it is true, but we need a larger circle of friends. Five at the least, seven max. Because antisocial. And what&#039;s that supposed to mean? I could make the jump in my sleep, nub. Copper didn&#039;t pay attention, he kept trotting passing his brother and coughing, saying loser while he did. You know the &quot;Coughlosercough&quot; Thing. Yeah.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1396668009";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff7700";s:9:"cha